                <h1>Celebrate National Native American Heritage Month</h1>
                <p>National Native American Heritage Month is a time to celebrate the rich cultures, histories, and contributions of Native American peoples. Observed in November, this month encourages education about indigenous traditions, promotes awareness of ongoing challenges, and honors the resilience and diversity of Native communities across the United States.</p>
